'''2013年伏尔加格勒公共汽车爆炸事件'''是2013年10月21日发生在[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[南部聯邦管區|南部聯邦管區]][[伏尔加格勒州|伏尔加格勒州]]的[[伏尔加格勒|伏尔加格勒市]]的一起[[自杀式袭击|自杀式袭击]]。这次爆炸由一名叫Naida Asiyalova({{lang|ru|Наида Сиражудиновна Асиялова}})的女性自杀式袭击者所为。她在一辆载有40人的公共汽车上引爆了所穿的炸弹背心。共造成车上包括肇事者在内的8人死亡，36人受伤。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rt.com/news/volgograd-bus-explosion-dead-486|title=At least 5 people die in bus explosion|publisher=Russia Today|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2013-10-21|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117093117/https://www.rt.com/news/volgograd-bus-explosion-dead-486/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24608694|title=A bus explosion killed 4 people in Russia|publisher=BBC News|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2013-10-21|archive-date=2013-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131229224311/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24608694|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/21/us-russia-blast-idUSBRE99K08G20131021|title=Russia bus explosion killed 4 people|publisher=Reuters|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2013-10-21|archive-date=2015-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015015711/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/21/us-russia-blast-idUSBRE99K08G20131021|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.itar-tass.com/c32/919858.html |title=Five dead, 27 injured in bus explosion in Volgograd region |accessdate=2013-12-29 |archive-date=2013-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022222136/http://www.itar-tass.com/c32/919858.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.ria.ru/russia/20131021/184272242/6-Killed-in-Bus-Bomb-Attack-in-SRussia-.html|title=Up to 6 Killed in Bus Bomb Blast in S.Russia – Officials|publisher=Ria Novosti|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2013-10-21|archive-date=2014-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730222544/http://en.ria.ru/russia/20131021/184272242/6-Killed-in-Bus-Bomb-Attack-in-SRussia-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

袭击者是来自[[达吉斯坦共和国|达吉斯坦共和国]]的30岁的女性Naida Asiyalova。此前被俄罗斯联邦执法机构通缉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/moscow-terrorist-blast-volgograd-509/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-29 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919030457/https://www.rt.com/news/moscow-terrorist-blast-volgograd-509/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>爆炸所用为500-600克TNT炸药。她的丈夫Dmitry Sokolov，是来自达吉斯坦共和国首都[[馬哈奇卡拉|馬哈奇卡拉]]的一名武装分子。

伏尔加格勒州当局宣布哀悼三天。市民为爆炸受害者献血。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/bus-blast-volgograd-russia-541 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-30 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024225115/https://www.rt.com/news/bus-blast-volgograd-russia-541/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==反应==
10月22日，[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]谴责伏尔加格勒公共汽车自杀式爆炸事件。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/china/2013-10/22/c_132821177.htm|title=China condemned Volgograd bus bombing|publisher=Xinhua News Agency|date=2013-10-22|accessdate=2013-10-22|archive-date=2013-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115190448/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/china/2013-10/22/c_132821177.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

11月16日，俄罗斯[[聯邦安全局|聯邦安全局]]在一次行动中打死5名武装分子，其中就包括Naida Asiyalova的丈夫。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/volgograd-bombing-sokolov-killed-833/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-29 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011630/https://www.rt.com/news/volgograd-bombing-sokolov-killed-833/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.ria.ru/crime/20131116/184751030/Militant-Behind-Volgograd-Suicide-Bombing-Killed-in-Russias-Dagestan.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-29 |archive-date=2014-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815210306/http://en.ria.ru/crime/20131116/184751030/Militant-Behind-Volgograd-Suicide-Bombing-Killed-in-Russias-Dagestan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/16/us-russia-dagestan-militants-idUSBRE9AF07I20131116 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-29 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924190901/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/16/us-russia-dagestan-militants-idUSBRE9AF07I20131116 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

